  "description": "Finance and material management system. The system consisted of 3 modules: Estimates, Purchases by estimate, and Finances. The main element of the project was tables. We used a fully functional table of our own design based on DTable.js. This table component could be supplemented with data formatters and all sorts of data processing before display, as well as the ability to edit data and save it to the server. I also used my own User Roles and Permissions (ACL) library, which was redesigned for Laravel and improved, so it became easy to monitor the status of applications.",
